                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-175-off926 t18250113-175-cd927"></join>, a quilt, value 2 s., and a bed-tick, value 3 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18250113-175-victim927" type="victimName">
                  John 
